ca Contemporary Record: Annual Survey and Documents: 1979\u20131980 |publisher=Africana Publishing Company |volume=XII |date=1981 |location=New York |isbn=978-0-8419-0160-5 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=May |first=Roy |last2=Furley |first2=Oliver |title=African Interventionist States |location=Milton, Vale of White Horse |publisher=Routledge |date=2017 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=0JU4DwAAQBAJ&dq= |isbn=978-1-351-75635-8 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Mmbando |first=S.I. |title=The Tanzania\u2013Uganda war in pictures | publisher=Longman Tanzania |date=1980 |location=Dar es Salaam |isbn=978-0-582-78534-2 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Mzirai |first=Baldwin |title=Kuzama kwa Idi Amin |publisher=Publicity International |date=1980 |location=Dar es Salaam |language=Swahili |oclc=9084117 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite journal| last = Nyeko| first = Balam| title =  Exile Politics and Resistance to Dictatorship: The Ugandan Anti-Amin Organizations in Zambia, 1972-79| journal =  African Affairs| volume = 96| issue = 382| date = January 1997| pages=95\u2013108| url = | doi = 10.1093/oxfordjournals.afraf.a007823 | ref = harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Pollack |first=Kenneth Michael |title=Arabs at War: Military Effectiveness, 1948\u20131991 |location=Lincoln, NE |publisher=[[University of Nebraska Press]] |date=2004 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=sSHYdGR_xvoC&dq= |isbn=978-0-8032-0686-1 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite journal |last=Posnett |first=Richard |title=Uganda after Amin |journal=The World Today |volume=36 |issue=4 |pages=147\u2013153 |date=April 1980 |jstor=40395418 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Roberts |first=George |chapter=The Uganda\u2013Tanzania War, the fall of Idi Amin, and the failure of African diplomacy, 1978\u20131979 |editor-last=Anderson |editor-first=David M. |editor-last2=Rolandsen |editor-first2=\u00d8ystein H. |title=Politics and Violence in Eastern Africa: The Struggles of Emerging States |publisher=Routledge |location=London |date=2017 |url=ht